
Lua-5.1.3 source code modifications:

  1. Applied the pushhstring patch

  2. Made the following adjustments in luaconf.h:

     //BZ#define LUA_NUMBER_DOUBLE
     #undef LUA_NUMBER_DOUBLE

     //BZ#define LUA_NUMBER  double
     #define LUA_NUMBER  float                                               

     //BZ#define LUA_NUMBER_SCAN "%lf"
     #define LUA_NUMBER_SCAN "%f"

  3. Moved the *.c files to *.cxx for C++ compilation
     (except for lua.c and luac.c)

*  6. GZIP'ed the following files:
     doc/*
     etc/*
     test/*
     src/lua.c
     src/luac.c

  5. Changed the return type of lua_toboolean from int to bool to prevent
     compiler performance warnings on Visual Studio 2005.

  9. Undefined (in include/luaconf.h):
       LUA_COMPAT_VARARG
       LUA_COMPAT_MOD
       LUA_COMPAT_LSTR
       LUA_COMPAT_GFIND
       LUA_COMPAT_OPENLIB

*  10. Added the following to lua.h  (and associated code)
        lua_set_fopen()
        lua_set_popen()
        lua_set_system()
        lua_set_remove()
        lua_set_rename()
